metadata.description: An abandoned diner interior with a row of metallic stools lined up against a wooden counter, yellow menu boards mounted on the wall, and a dusty, worn tile floor scattered with debris. The space features a ceiling fan, a soda fountain, and signs of neglect, including faded signage and disrepair. The mood is desolate and decaying, evoking nostalgia for a once-bustling eatery now left to decay, with no human activity present.
